Example.Why:
This works because: (1) plan skeleton is presented before execution — Plan-and-Solve contract
    honored; (2) every recommendation cites a specific UX law (Fitts's Law, Hick's Law, Jakob's Law,
    progressive disclosure); (3) specifications include exact numeric values (49pt, 44x44pt, 4.5:1);
    (4) accessibility is integrated throughout all four POUR principles, not appended; (5) validation
    plan includes specific task scripts, sample size rationale, and numeric success thresholds;
    (6) iOS-specific language is consistent throughout (pt units, UITabBar, Face ID, VoiceOver).
